<item>
            <title>[CXF-6677] Content-Type is empty on POST request with empty body </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-6677</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have following code:&lt;br/&gt;
endpoint:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;@Path(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
@Produces(MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON)
@Consumes(MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON)
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; MyApi
{
	@Path(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;invoices/{number}/bookkeep&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
	@PUT
	&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; bookkeep(@PathParam(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;number&quot;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; invoiceNumber);
        ...

}&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;client configuration:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;JAXRSClientFactoryBean bean = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; JAXRSClientFactoryBean();
bean.setAddress(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;http:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//localhost&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;bean.setInheritHeaders(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;);
bean.setThreadSafe(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;);
bean.setServiceClass(MyApi.class);
MyApi myApi = bean.create(MyApi.class);&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When I run&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;myApi.bookkeep(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;111&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Result:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;Http-Method: PUT
Content-Type: 
Headers: {Access-Token=[aaa], Accept=[application/json]}&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Expected: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;...
Content-Type: application/json
...&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;With cxf-rt-rs-client version 3.0.3 Content-Type is application/json.&lt;br/&gt;
With cxf-rt-rs-client version 3.1.4 Content-Type is empty.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
